If additional init containers are needed in the same pod (such as additional metrics or logging exporters), they can be defined using the *initContainers* parameter. Here is an example:

~~~
initContainers:
  - name: your-image-name
    image: your-image
    imagePullPolicy: Always
    ports:
      - name: portname
        containerPort: 1234
~~~
